{{ill|Nagahata clan|ja|長幡部連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shidori clan|ja|倭文部|1=Shidori clan|2=ja|3=倭文氏|4=zh|5=倭文氏|6=de|7=Shizuri Clan|8=fr|9=Clan Shizuri|lt=Shizuri Bemin (vassals of the Shizuri clan)|lt=Shidori clan|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tanabe clan|ja|田辺宿禰|12=draft}}, {{ill|Takehara clan|ja|竹原氏|12=draft}}, {{ill|Okura clan|ja|巨椋連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ōkura Okihajime clan|ja|大椋置始連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Imaki clan|ja|今木連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Yuge clan|ja|弓削氏|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tame clan|ja|多米連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Minu clan|ja|美努連|12=draft}} ({{ill|Minokuni Rulers|ja|三野県主|12=draft}}), {{ill|Tottoribe clan|ja|鳥取部連|12=draft}}, {{ill|Jingu clan|ja|神宮部造|12=draft}}, {{ill|Agatanoinukai clan|ja|県犬養氏|1=Agata no Inukai clan|12=draft}}

