|image = Bentenjima on Inasa Beach.jpg|right|thumb|250x250px|
caption = {{ill|Inasa Beach|ja|稲佐浜|12=draft}} ([[:ja:稲佐の浜|稲佐の浜]] ''Inasa-no-hama'') in {{ill|Izumo, Shimane|lt=Izumo|en|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shimane Prefecture|en}}, where the myth places Ōkuninushi's meeting with the messengers of heaven and his surrender to them.|cult_centre={{ill|Shizuri Shrines|ja|倭文神社|12=draft}}
