In ''{{ill|Kogo Shūi|ja|古語拾遺|12=draft}}'', she is called the '''far ancestor of the {{ill|Shizuri clan|ja|倭文部|1=Shizuri clan|2=ja|3=倭文氏|4=zh|5=倭文氏|6=de|7=Shizuri Clan|8=fr|9=Clan Shizuri|lt=Shizuri Bemin (vassals of the Shizuri clan)|lt=Shizuri clan|12=draft}}'''. In ''{{ill|Sendai Kujihongi|ja|先代旧事本紀|12=draft}}'', she is described as the '''distant ancestor of the {{ill|Shidori-no-Mikoto|ja|倭文造|12=draft}}'''.

